HEADWORD: Umbles
<hw>Um"bles</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Nombles</er>.]</ety> <def>The entrails and coarser parts of a deer;
hence, sometimes, entrails, in general.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>humbles</asp>.]</altsp> <rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
